        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Han Seung Ju has chosen to stay single. She cannot afford to get married, nor is she confident that she wants to. However, certain events transpire which cause her to fear being alone, and she finds herself needing the safety and status that only the perception of a marriage can bring. Seung Ju decides to hire a man to be a stand-in husband, and the man she chooses is O Jak Du.\n\nThrough meeting O Jak Du, will Han Seung Ju find true love and happiness?\n\nEdit Translation\n\nEnglish\n\n한국어\n\n中文(简体)\n\nРусский",
